title: House GOP Withdraws Trump Health Care Bill

organizations.name: house gop withdraws trump health care bill

text:
WASHINGTON (CBS SF & AP) — The House of Representatives recessed Friday without the vote demanded by President Donald Trump on his health care plan to replace ObamaCare.
With the outcome uncertain, the House Republicans chose to withdraw health care bill and head into a special meeting to discuss the plan’s future.
